<para style="p">For the chief musician; set to Al Tashheth. A psalmof David. A michtam; when he fled from Saul, in the cave.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Be merciful to me, God, be merciful to me,</para>

<para style="q1">for I take refuge in you until these troubles are over.</para>

<para style="q1">I stay under your wings for protection until this destruction is over.</para>
